import 'react-pro-sidebar/dist/css/styles.css';
import { useAppState } from "../service/AppStateContext.tsx";
import { Container, Nav, Navbar, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';
import "../App.css"


export const NaveMenu = () => {
    const { state } = useAppState();
    console.log("****state", state);
    return (
        <>

                    <Navbar.Brand href="/">מעיין הבירה</Navbar.Brand>
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                    <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                        <Nav className="me-auto">
                            <Nav.Link href="/">בית</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="/tables">שולחנות</Nav.Link>
                            <NavDropdown title="תפריט" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="/menus">תפריט מלא</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="/menus/starter">מנות ראשונות</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="/menus/Soups">מרקים</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="/menus/MainCourse">מנה עיקרית</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="/menus/desserts">קינוחים</NavDropdown.Item>

                            <NavDropdown title="לקוחות" id="basic-nav-dropdown">

                            </NavDropdown>
                            <Nav.Link href="#deets">More deets</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link eventKey={2} href="#memes">
                                Dank memes
                            </Nav.Link>
                        </Nav>
                    </Navbar.Collapse>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
        </>
    );
};

export default NaveMenu;
